Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:08.42,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\b1\3c&H7A777B&\pos(960,1000)}In time, losing consciousness, organs, fins, and eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.12,0:00:13.29,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Male and female merge into a single life form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.73,0:00:19.93,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}A torn goldfish scooping net,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:26.34,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}The lantern’s dim light rolls, peeking through as it bleeds\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.01,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}My soaked hair drips
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:40.09,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I wanted the festival music in the air to be far away\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:42.69,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Go far away, toward where no one is
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:52.63,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}In this sea, humans become coral, \Nswallowed by the void and infinite darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:55.37,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Paradise lies deep below
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.37,0:00:59.84,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Don't let go, hold me and sink
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:04.21,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}To the depths where even the moon can’t be scooped 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:08.58,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:15.69,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I wish I could light a love in the pitch-black abyss\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:18.62,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Let's drift together\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.62,0:01:25.20,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}In the future we won't be alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:30.70,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}We'll become "us," melting together as we live on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:33.87,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}You will join with me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:36.98,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}And I will eventually transform into "us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.98,0:01:40.88,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}As if flowing, our two lives sink into one body
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:44.78,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Until we reach the field of graves
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:49.62,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}With no destination, and not knowing how to return
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:55.63,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}A one-way ticket, guided by a lantern called hope\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:02:03.34,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Time moves on, the journey continues\NLet's dive deeper, let's go on without fearing the darkness\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:07.34,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Even if we never find what we’re looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:10.24,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:18.88,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I hope I'm buried beneath corpses falling headfirst into the future\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:22.79,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}If you wish for it, look. An encore\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:28.33,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}This corpse can be revived at any time\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:33.40,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Even if it's ugly, it melts and lives on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:36.20,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}The moon is just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:41.01,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}A lantern hung by the Earth, isn't it?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:42.54,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Ah, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:47.41,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}We were already one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:55.22,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Floating, sinking, even if we're clumsy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:59.93,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I just want to live
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:06.97,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish	
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:14.07,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I wish I could light a love in the pitch-black abyss\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.07,0:03:18.14,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish	
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:26.69,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}I hope I’m buried beneath corpses falling headfirst into the future\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:30.79,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish	
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:40.53,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}We’re moving forward, relying on hope\NIt's okay if we can't return
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.53,0:03:44.87,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Just like a deep-sea anglerfish, where to?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.84,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Let's go as far as we can\N
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:54.51,YTGlow,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1000)\b1\3c&H7A777B&}Remaining as "us"\NJust living on
